snippet.textDisplay: Afreen or Afrin is derives from *_Middle Persian_* *𐭠𐭯𐭥𐭩𐭭 āfrīn* _"praise, blessing"_ and is also the present tense form of the verb *âfaridan* _"to create"_ . The expression has been translated by some as _"praise to the creator!"._
